00:00:00.250 --> 00:00:04.790
In today’s video, we will run through the
satirical horror movie American Psycho from

00:00:04.790 --> 00:00:09.900
2000, where a wealthy New York City investment
banking executive, Patrick Bateman, hides

00:00:09.900 --> 00:00:15.330
his alternate psychopathic ego from his co-workers
and friends as he delves deeper into his violent,

00:00:15.330 --> 00:00:17.020
hedonistic fantasies.

